  "text": "The method here described has the sensitivity of the reversed RID-teehnique, utilizing purified viral antigen eoupled to erythro eytes and eomplement-mediated immunohaemolysis in agarose gels. This was introdueed with the speeifie aim of obtaining more information about the nature of haemolytie antibodies of rahbit orgine and alsa human sera containing haemolytie antibodies for sheep, bovine and human erythroeytes [CITATION_1] .",
